OL,3,CSwansea MP 'embarrassed' about culture
OL,4,Cat troubled fire services in Wales
OL,6,FCredit: Parliament Live TV.
OL,8,FSwansea East MP Carolyn Harris has
OL,9,Ftold a Parliament committee she is
OL,10,F"embarrassed" about the culture at
OL,11,Fboth South Wales and North Wales fire
OL,12,Fand rescue services.
OL,14,FHer comments come just days after ITV
OL,15,FWales revealed how the man brought in
OL,16,Fto head up the service in South Wales
OL,17,Fis himself at the centre of bullying
OL,18,Fallegations.
