OL,3,CSwansea MP 'embarrassed' about culture
OL,4,Cat troubled fire services in Wales
OL,6,FMs Harris told the Women and
OL,7,FEqualities Committee: "You would have
OL,8,Fseen the investigation that Paul Brand
OL,9,Fdid for ITV, two fire services in
OL,10,FWales which I am extremely embarrassed
OL,11,Fby.
OL,13,F"It's not a minor problem, it is a
OL,14,Fmajor problem and I think it is
OL,15,Fprobably worse in the fire service
OL,16,Fthan anywhere else, from the research
OL,17,Fthat I have done."
