OL,3,CSwansea MP 'embarrassed' about culture
OL,4,Cat troubled fire services in Wales
OL,6,FShe then posed a question to Kathryn
OL,7,FBilling, Equality, Diversity and
OL,8,FInclusion Lead at the National Fire
OL,9,FChiefs Council, asking her: "How do
OL,10,Fyou combat that?"
OL,12,FMs Billing replied: "I think the one
OL,13,Fthing that we are all talking about
OL,14,Fhere is that this is systemic. We are
OL,15,Fbattling against an institution.
OL,17,F"In the conversations that I regularly
OL,18,Fhave with colleagues in the police as
OL,19,Fwell, I have been in the service for
OL,20,F25 years and things, in fairness, have
OL,21,Fmoved on.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
