PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F469A1708633976
OL,3,CSwansea MP 'embarrassed' about culture
OL,4,Cat troubled fire services in Wales
OL,6,F"The conversations and banter have
OL,7,Fsignificantly changed but it is still
OL,8,Fnot to the level and we are certainly
OL,9,Fstill seeing cases where it certainly
OL,10,Fhasn't moved on.
OL,12,F"This is absolutely going down to the
OL,13,Freal basics because we have built an
OL,14,Finstitution on probably white,
OL,15,Fheterosexual, male-dominated
OL,16,Fsystems... processes, uniform,
OL,17,Fequipment - every single thing is
OL,18,Fbuilt around one particular viewpoint."
