OL,3,CSwansea MP 'embarrassed' about culture
OL,4,Cat troubled fire services in Wales
OL,6,FShe believes that needs to be broken
OL,7,Fdown and told the committee about some
OL,8,Fof the work being done by the NFCC
OL,9,Faround looking at policies and
OL,10,Fprocesses.
OL,12,FMs Billing said: "Having broader
OL,13,Fconversations about how do we bring
OL,14,Fthe victim's voice into the
OL,15,Fdevelopment of recruitment,
OL,16,Fdevelopment of policies, and
OL,17,Fdevelopment leadership programmes?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
