OL,3,CSwansea MP 'embarrassed' about culture
OL,4,Cat troubled fire services in Wales
OL,6,F"Because, until we can start to view
OL,7,Fthings from the victims, but also
OL,8,Fother people's perspectives, we will
OL,9,Fprobably continue."
OL,11,FShe added: "It's that thing, if you
OL,12,Falways do what you have always done,
OL,13,Fyou will always get what you've always
OL,14,Fgot. So how can we now bring in
OL,15,Fdifferent viewpoints? And that comes
OL,16,Fback to that: a more diverse workforce.
OL,18,F"What we need to do is make sure we
OL,19,Fare bringing them into an organisation
OL,20,Fwhere they will absolutely (feel)
OL,21,Fvalued and their voices will be heard."
